<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I have found an error in Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Abstract's _dsn method.
Input parameters should be filtered before converting to the DSN string.</p>

<p>This issue was found when I tried to use Zend_Queue with PostgreSQL database (ZF-7827).</p>

<p>To resolve this issue we should add a list with available connection parameters to every Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_* class and check parameters before assembly the DSN string.</p>

<p>The following links can be used as a reference:
<a href="http://ru.php.net/manual/en/ref.pdo-pgsql.connection.php">http://ru.php.net/manual/en/…</a>
<a href="http://ru.php.net/manual/en/ref.pdo-mysql.connection.php">http://ru.php.net/manual/en/…</a></p>

